message.body: Oooo yea! I get done at 4:30. Is that too late?
Well i might go earlier than that. But will still be there then to meet up! I will let you know where once i figure it out
Ok kewl. How was Iowa? And your interview?
Hey sugar. We are at clear lake. I am not sure how late we will stay though so we might want to do a beach day another day with you and me.
That sounds good. I have a few other things tonight although I wish I was on the beach! Are you out of town this weekend?
I am in town but doing wedding stuff on friday and sat. Do you work everyday of the week?
Yep... :( but I'm free nights and weekends! More tacos!
